  <head><lb/>peruṅkatai</head>
  <head type="sub"><lb/>mutalāvatu uñcaik kāṇṭam.</head>
  <div type="mulam">
    <head type="sub"><lb/>32 — karuṭu peyarttatu.</head>
    <head type="sub"><lb/>(piraccōtaṉaṉai nōkki utayaṇaṉ kūṟal)</head>
    <lg>
      <l><lb/>...............<note place="foot">itaṟku muṉṉuḷḷa pakutikaḷ kiṭaikkavillai.</note><hi rend="bold">po</hi>ruḷ puri nūlum</l>
     <l><lb/>alakai cāṉṟa vulaka purāṇamum</l>
      <l><lb/>palavakai marapiṟ pācaṇ ṭiyarkaḷ</l>
    </lg>
  </div>
  <div type="urai">
    <head><lb/>kuṟippurai</head>
    <head type="sub">32 — karaṭu peyarttatu.</head>
    <head type="sub">karaṭu – yāṉaiyiṉ mataccerukku.</head>
<p><lb/>[utayaṇaṉ piraccōtaṉaṉuṭaiya viruppattiṉpaṭi avaṉatu
  <lb/>paṭṭattu yāṉaiyiṉ mataccērukkai aṭakkiyūrntatum, appōḻatu
  <lb/>avaṉ aṉpu pārāṭṭiyatum, utayaṇaṉum vācavatattaiyum oruvarai
  <lb/>yoruvar nōkkik kāḻaṟṟatum, piṟavum ippatutiyāl aṟiyalātam,]</p>
    <list rend="numbered">
      <item><lb/>poruḷpurināl - artta cāttiram</item>
      <item><lb/>alakai - aḷavu, uraiyāṇi; ulakapurāṇam - ulakattiṉ
        <lb/>paḻaiya varalāṟṟaik kūṟum tūl; ulōka vilācaṉiyeṉavum vaḻaṅ
        <lb/>kappeṟum.</item>
      <item><lb/>pācaṇṭiyarkaḷ - pāṣaṇṭiyarkaḷ; ivarkaḷ toṇṇāṟ
        <lb/>rāṟu camaya cāttirat tarukkak kōvaiyaiyuṭaiyarātaviṉ, ‘palavakai
        <lb/>marapiṟ pācaṇṭiyarkaḷ’ eṉṟār; <hi rend="bold">cilap.</hi> 6; <num xml:lang="en">14 - 5</num>-ām. aṭi.
        <lb/>kaḷukku <hi rend="bold">aṭiyārkkunallā</hi>reḻutiya  vicēṭavuraiyaiyum avaṟṟiṉ
        <lb/>kīḻkkuṟippaiyum pārkka.</item>
    </list>
  </div>
